articles.author: PTI
articles.title: Another South African cheetah translocated to Kuno National Park dies - Deccan Herald
articles.description: One of the cheetahs translocated to Madhya Pradesh's Kuno National Park (KNP) from South Africa died on Sunday, a senior forest official said. The deceased cheetah 'Uday' aged six years. Notably, this is the second such incident at KNP in almost a month. Also…
